porkbind 2.0
============
Implement gethostbyname_r with autoconf
Make option to disable zone transfer and recursive query tests
Rearrange mutexes for optimal locking
Commmand line option for RECURSIVE_QUERY_TEST_DOMAIN
Add all CVE's to porkbind.conf (not just CERT alerts)
..see table at bottom of http://www.isc.org/index.pl?/sw/bind/bind-security.php
doxygen

